J. Gay, Erysim.
</taxonomicName>
<bibCitation id="F18D8D67FF918361FAC45BB5FA1AFC16" box="[1280,1418,980,1005]" page="5" pageId="44" pageNumber="44" score="2.2452908429188243" volumeTitle="Nov." year="1842">Nov.: 5. 1842</bibCitation>
